        <h4 class="card-title">
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#cigaccwlcs">Can I get a credit card with low cibil score?</a>
        </h4>
        <div id="cigaccwlcs" class="collapse">
          <p>Credit card is the most conveninent type of payment method in today's world, in which you can buy the items you want and pay for them later.</p>
          <p>Credit card can be of good use if used properly and repayment of it done on time.</p>
          <p>The issue with its repayment will directly affect your cibil score.</p>
          <p>Sometimes due to issues we might get irregular with the repayment which gets us into the category of low cibil scorers.</p>
          <p>But you can get a credit card with low cibil score with these options:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Applying with your primary bank</li>
            <p>Applying for credit card with your bank can be easy because your primary bank will have your financial history which makes them easy  to trust which makes you an easy applicant for credit card.</p>
            <li>Get a secured credit card</li>
            <p>Credit cards are usually given to a person without taking any collateral from them .But in case of bad credit credit card is prevented.</p>
            <p>So what you can do is provide a collateral against which bank will provide you with a credit card.</p>
          </ul>
          <p>There are cons of taking a credit card with bad credit score which are.,</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Getting a credit card with a high rate of interest.</li>
            <li>Low credit limit.</li>
            <li>High possibility for card rejection.</li>
          </ul>
